 {
  coords 2044.063 3.122 828.46
  m_sTitle "SITUATION"
  m_sTextData "Our unit is in a staging position (GRID REF:015 023) preparing to conduct a river crossing."\
  "We are an understrength company sized group, armed with PKMs, AK74s, SVDs and RPGs.  We have brought a bmp1 along for fire support. We have no dedicated crew. Our unit has access to a FPV kit with 4x drones, 2 are RPG armed and 2 are unarmed for ISR. This is available in a box near the spawn, and can be given to whoever CO desires. Recommend PSG."\
  ""\
  "Enemy is a platoon sized infantry unit, armed with L85s, GPMGs, Carl Gustavs and DMRs. Wearing multicam camo. They have access to night vision devices and ISR drones."\
  ""\
  "Command has tasked us with seizing a route across the river to enable an assault by follow on forces onto a nearby town being used to stage supplies for this section of the front."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 {
